title: Electoral fraud
deleted: ==Voter fraud in the United States presidential election 2020==

There is reasonable suspision of voter fraud committed in several battle ground states in the US to keep President Donald J. Trump from being reelected. The most prominent cases occurred in Wisconsin, Pensylvania and Arizona.
